{{!-- Upper header content on homepage --}}
<h1>{{title}}</h1>
<div class="missionStatement">
    <p>Our concept is simple: The World can be hard. It can knock you down and sometimes you can’t find you way back
        onto your feet.
        <br>At {{title}}, at your fingertips are the words and powerful emotions of mankind’s most inspirational
        speakers, influencers and humanitarians.
        <br>They’re all here with one mission: to Inspire you, to motivate you, and to remind you of the power of words
        and the compassion of the human spirit.</p>

    <p>That’s not all -- you’ll be able to connect with people from around the world and share your own inspirations.
        <br>Not a wordsmith? No problem, simply send some of your favorite quotes to help people through the tough
        times. Because remember:</p>
</div>
<p class="homeQuote">“You cannot do a kindness too soon, for you never know how soon it will be too late.”
    <br>-Ralph Waldo Emerson, American Author</p>

